      {
        "type": "email",
        "html": "<p>Good morning, {first_name, \"lovely subscriber\"},</p><p>Welcome to the very first edition of Morning Conference — the morning newsletter for subscribers of <em>One Man &amp; His Blog. </em>I had this idea late last year, but unfortunately, the closure of schools put pay to my plans to launch in January.</p><p>Here's the idea: this is a short, sharp morning email, to help you catch up on the media and publishing related news that might be useful to you in your work. I'll give you a little context on each story, and let you decide if it's relevant.</p><p>In a way, I'm giving you a glimpse into my “notebook”, at the sort of information I'm using to inform my training and consulting work.</p><p>Feedback, as ever, gratefully received.</p>"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
