      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "While I can see why Facebook is doing this, and why it might seem like an attractive idea to do this from some creators' point of view, the idea of the whole — or even a substantial chunk — of my income being dependent on Facebook's good will brings me out in hives. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "I see no sign here that Facebook will make it easy to move your subscribers, and their billing details, if you ever moved platform. Risky. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
